data.description: Sought after Encino Park sits this single story home on .3 lot size....beautiful mature live oak trees with a great curb appeal! No low ball offers please, home is priced according to condition and lot size.  3/2 with almost 2200 sf, hardwood floors, saltillo flooring, and little carpet to deal with. Very flexible floorplan. Backyard is large enough to garden, or add a pool! Garage is oversized. Back in 2014 all windows were replaced too! Home will need some TLC and new appliances, but with a little work, this place will shine!  COME SEE TODAY. Be the least expensive home in the neighborhood!
